// gelin (Input) Function Example // This example shows how to use gelin to get user input // First, let's print a brief explanation

bandhig("gelin Example - User Input in Soplang")
bandhig(" --------------------------------- ")
// Using gelin to get the user's name

door magac = gelin("Enter your name: ")
// Display a greeting with the entered name

bandhig("Hello, " + magac + "!")
bandhig("Welcome to Soplang programming!")
// Show the type of the input (always a string)

bandhig("The type of your input is: " + nooc(magac))
// Example of simple input processing

bandhig("Your name has several characters.")
// Thank the user

bandhig("Thank you for trying gelin in Soplang!")